description: A player in a red jersey takes a three-point shot from the top of the key which misses off the backboard and rim.
Player #7 for the Green Team secures the defensive rebound after the missed three-point shot.
Player #7 for the Green Team attempts a mid-range jump shot from the right wing which misses.
The Green Team player who got the rebound attempts an immediate putback shot in the paint which is missed.
A player for the Red Team attempts a shot in the paint which is blocked by Green Team player #4.
On the left court, the player in the red jersey #2 drives to the basket and misses a layup.
On the left court, the player in the green jersey #4 secures the defensive rebound after the missed layup.
On the left court, the player in the green jersey #7 attempts a three-point shot from the left wing and misses.
On the left court, the player in the red jersey #5 grabs the defensive rebound.
On the right court, the player in the green jersey #2 misses a three-point shot from the right wing.
On the right court, the player in the red jersey #5 secures the defensive rebound.
On the left court, the player in the red jersey #8 misses a close-range shot in the paint.
On the left court, the player in the green jersey #8 gets the defensive rebound.
On the left court, the player in the green jersey #4 misses a three-point shot from the top of the key.
On the left court, the player in the red jersey #0 grabs the defensive rebound.
On the right court, the player in the red jersey #1 misses a mid-range jump shot from the right elbow.
On the right court, the player in the green jersey #4 secures the defensive rebound.
On the left court, the player in the green jersey #8 blocks a shot attempt from the player in the red jersey #8.
On the left court, the player in the red jersey #2 makes a putback shot in the paint.
On the right court, the player in the green jersey #4 passes to a teammate who immediately scores a three-pointer.
On the right court, the player in the green jersey #2 makes a catch-and-shoot three-pointer from the right wing.
On the left court, the player in the green jersey #4 misses a three-point shot from the top of the key.
